Package ca.projectTOMi.tomi.exception

Provides classes for handling unexpected values.

See: Description

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ClientNotFoundException
    A requested Client was unavailable.
    EmptyProjectListException
    No Projects are returned from the database.
    EntryNotFoundException
    A requested Entry was unavailable.
    ExpenseNotFoundException
    A requested Expense was unavailable.
    IllegalEntryStateException
    The requested Entry could not be updated because it was not in a valid state.
    IllegalTimesheetModificationException
    An attempt to modify a timesheet was made in a fashion in which the timesheet was unable to process.
    InvalidIDPrefixException
    A provided id prefix is invalid.
    MinimumAdminAccountException
    An attempt was made to reduce the number of admin accounts below the required minimum number.
    MinimumProgramDirectorAccountException
    An attempt was made to reduce the number of program director accounts below the required minimum number.
    ProjectNotFoundException
    A requested Project was unavailable.
    TaskNotFoundException
    A requested Task was unavailable.
    TeamNotFoundException
    A requested Team was unavailable.
    TimesheetNotFoundException
    A requested Timesheet was unavailable.
    UnitTypeNotFoundException
    A requested UnitType was unavailable.
    UserAccountNotFoundException
    A requested UserAccount was unavailable.
